        <p class="specialty-description">Diagnóstico y tratamiento de acidez, regurgitación y dolor torácico asociados al reflujo ácido.</p>
        <div class="specialty-treatments">
          <span>Endoscopía digestiva</span>
          <span>pH-metría esofágica</span>
          <span>Tratamiento farmacológico</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="specialty-card transition-item" data-delay="200">
        <div class="specialty-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 10h4v4h-4z"></path><circle cx="7" cy="9" r="3"></circle><path d="M13 21v-5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H4a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v5"></path><path d="M13 21h8"></path><path d="M13 17h8"></path></svg>
